# Mosquitto ACL — Desk Beacon System

# Backend server — full access
user backend
topic readwrite desk/#
topic readwrite gateway/#
topic readwrite user/#
topic readwrite system/#
topic read $SYS/#

# Gateway service accounts — pattern: gateway-{gatewayId}
# Add per-gateway entry during provisioning via provision-beacon.sh
# Example:
# user gateway-gw-warsaw-1
# topic readwrite desk/#
# topic write gateway/gw-warsaw-1/#
# topic read $SYS/#

# Beacon accounts — pattern: beacon-{hardwareId}
# Added automatically by scripts/provision-beacon.sh
# Example:
# user beacon-d-abc123
# topic write desk/DESK_ID/checkin
# topic write desk/DESK_ID/status
# topic write desk/DESK_ID/qr_scan
# topic read  desk/DESK_ID/command
# topic read  desk/DESK_ID/config
